Example:

B0: 1 as you can only have one partition of zero element set
B1: 1 as you can only have one partition of one element set {a}.
B2: 2
       {a}{b}
       {a,b}
B3: 5
       {a}{b}{c}
       {a,b}{c}
       {a}{b,c}
       {a,c}{b}
       {a,b,c}
B4: 15
       {a}{b}{c}{d}
       {a,b,c,d}
       {a,b}{c,d}
       {a,c}{b,d}
       {a,d}{b,c}
       {a,b}{c}{d}
       {a,c}{b}{d}
       {a,d}{b}{c}
       {b,c}{a}{d}
       {b,d}{a}{c}
       {c,d}{a}{b}
       {a}{b,c,d}
       {b}{a,c,d}
       {c}{a,b,d}
       {d}{a,b,c}

